    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the submitted evidence package and determined that the simulation results are sufficiently credible to support the COU decision. Seven factors were assessed and all were found to meet or exceed requirements appropriate for MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with the MRL 2 scoping determination. The overall evidence base supports acceptance of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
